code .
npm install --save-dev @babel/core @babel/cli @babel/preset-env @babel/node -> to install babel -> it converts ES6 code to ES5
npm install --save-dev nodemon -> to install nodemon - node monitor
create .babelrc file
start in scripts in package.json file
npm run start -> to execute main file

npm update -> to update packages
build,update ->add in scripts in package.json as "npm update

type in cmd -> npm run build
"npm run" look for scripts tag and run that command and execute "npm update"